Package: vpstheme
Type: Package
Title: A collection of themes and functions for R users in the VPS
Version: 2.3.3
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sam", "Gow", email = "sam.gow@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: The main purpose of vpstheme is to enable R users in the Victorian Public Service to use the colours and fonts defined in the [Brand Victoria Guidelines](https://www.vic.gov.au/brand-victoria-guidelines) to create compliant visualisations in ggplot.
